<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>That Song Admin</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        /* Google Fonts - Noto Sans KR 추가 */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

        /* 기본 폰트 설정 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }

        /* 다크 모드 스타일 */
        .dark-mode {
            background-color: #1f2937; /* 다크 배경색 */
            color: #d1fae5; /* 민트 텍스트 */
        }

        .dark-mode a {
            color: #6ee7b7;
        }

        .dark-mode a:hover {
            color: #34d399;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="dark-mode font-sans">
<div class="flex min-h-screen">
    <!-- 사이드바 -->
    {{>sidebar}}

    <!-- 메인 콘텐츠 -->
    <main class="flex-1 p-6 transition-all duration-300 md:pl-12 md:pr-12">
        <header class="flex justify-between items-center pb-4 border-b border-teal-700">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">아티스트 수정</h1>
            <a href="/admin/artists" class="px-4 py-2 bg-teal-700 text-white rounded hover:bg-teal-600">
                목록 보기
            </a>
        </header>

        <section class="mt-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">아티스트 정보 수정</h2>
            {{#artist}}
                <form action="/admin/artists/{{id}}/edit" method="POST"
                      class="space-y-4 bg-teal-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div>
                        <label for="nameKr" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">이름 (한글)</label>
                        <input type="text" id="nameKr" name="nameKr" value="{{nameKr}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="nameEn" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">이름 (영문)</label>
                        <input type="text" id="nameEn" name="nameEn" value="{{nameEn}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="code" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">코드</label>
                        <input type="text" id="code" name="code" value="{{code}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200" readonly>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">타입</label>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <label class="inline-flex items-center">
                                <input type="radio" name="isGroup" value="true" {{#isGroup}}checked{{/isGroup}}
                                       class="form-radio text-teal-600">
                                <span class="ml-2 text-teal-200">그룹</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="inline-flex items-center">
                                <input type="radio" name="isGroup" value="false" {{^isGroup}}checked{{/isGroup}}
                                       class="form-radio text-teal-600">
                                <span class="ml-2 text-teal-200">솔로</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">활동 여부</label>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <label class="inline-flex items-center">
                                <input type="radio" name="isActive" value="true" {{#isActive}}checked{{/isActive}}
                                       class="form-radio text-teal-600">
                                <span class="ml-2 text-teal-200">활동 중</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="inline-flex items-center">
                                <input type="radio" name="isActive" value="false" {{^isActive}}checked{{/isActive}}
                                       class="form-radio text-teal-600">
                                <span class="ml-2 text-teal-200">미활동</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="debutDate" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">데뷔일</label>
                        <input type="date" id="debutDate" name="debutDate" value="{{debutDate}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="createdAt" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">최초 등록 시간</label>
                        <input type="datetime-local" id="createdAt" name="createdAt" value="{{createdAt}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200" disabled>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="updatedAt" class="block text-teal-200 font-bold mb-2">마지막 수정 시간</label>
                        <input type="datetime-local" id="updatedAt" name="updatedAt" value="{{updatedAt}}"
                               class="w-full p-2 rounded border border-teal-700 bg-teal-800 text-teal-200" disabled>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
                        <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-2 bg-teal-700 text-white rounded hover:bg-teal-600">
                            수정하기
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                <section class="mt-6">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">앨범 목록</h2>
                    <table class="table-auto w-full bg-teal-900 shadow-md rounded-lg">
                        <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-teal-700 text-teal-200">
                            <th class="p-2 border">아이디</th>
                            <th class="p-2 border">이름</th>
                            <th class="p-2 border">아티스트</th>
                            <th class="p-2 border">타입</th>
                            <th class="p-2 border">작업</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                        {{#albums}}
                            <tr class="hover:bg-teal-800">
                                <td class="p-2 border text-center">{{id}}</td>
                                <td class="p-2 border text-center">
                                    <a href="/admin/albums/{{id}}" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">
                                        {{name}}
                                    </a>
                                </td>
                                <td class="p-2 border text-center">
                                    {{artistName}}</td>
                                <td class="p-2 border text-center">{{type}} {{#isRepackage}}리패키지{{/isRepackage}}</td>
                                <td class="p-2 border text-center">
                                    <a href="/admin/albums/{{id}}/delete" class="text-red-500 hover:underline">삭제</a>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        {{/albums}}
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </section>
            {{/artist}}
            {{^artist}}
                아티스트 정보를 찾을 수 없습니다.
            {{/artist}}
        </section>
    </main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
